s.text: And I trace that false banana to the Nature's Plus Spiru-tein High Protein Energy Meal Banana Yogurt Coated Bar, which, although it ranked decently in terms of taste and texture going down, was no treat during the run.
It wasn't until I released two massive belches (each smelling strongly of false banana) that I was able to settle into the run and feel halfway normal.
Although we ate them as directed (30 minutes before exercising), they churned in my stomach with disturbing violence.
